00:12:03.390 --> 00:12:06.725
Busta Rhymes said, they changed
everything, fashion, style,

00:12:06.725 --> 00:12:08.920
the relationship of black
people and white people.

00:12:08.920 --> 00:12:10.835
I would say, yeah,
