00:12:40.688 --> 00:12:41.490
OK, I'll try it.

00:12:41.490 --> 00:12:45.380
He said, yo, but don't do it
as DMC, the famous celebrity

00:12:45.380 --> 00:12:46.400
rapper guy.

00:12:46.400 --> 00:12:48.130
Do it as little
Darryl McDaniels,

00:12:48.130 --> 00:12:50.600
the kid who loved
comic books first.

00:12:50.600 --> 00:12:51.520
And I said, OK, cool.

00:12:51.520 --> 00:12:54.540
Then he just basically said,
next week, come to my office.

00:12:54.540 --> 00:12:56.230
I got somebody I
want you to meet.

00:12:56.230 --> 00:12:57.610
