00:13:26.290 --> 00:13:28.040
So I'm like, OK, I got
to keep my game on.

00:13:28.040 --> 00:13:29.730
I don't even know
what I'm talking about

00:13:29.730 --> 00:13:31.750
and who I'm talking
about this with.

00:13:31.750 --> 00:13:35.220
And we opened the door, there
is D with his big Kool-Aid smile

00:13:35.220 --> 00:13:37.220
on the other side of the
door, like mad excited.

00:13:37.220 --> 00:13:39.886
DARRYL "DMC" MCDANIELS: Cause he
was like this is the comic book

00:13:39.886 --> 00:13:40.470
guy, right?

00:13:40.470 --> 00:13:41.830
EDGARDO MIRANDA-RODRIGUEZ:
I had no idea what we were

00:13:41.830 --> 00:13:43.670
about to talk about, right?

00:13:43.670 --> 00:13:45.300
And then he goes into
