00:14:04.200 --> 00:14:05.950
So we're kind of like
thinking about this.

00:14:05.950 --> 00:14:08.579
And we realized we
need to literally think

00:14:08.579 --> 00:14:09.245
about this more.

00:14:09.245 --> 00:14:11.411
And I told him from the
beginning, I was like, look,

00:14:11.411 --> 00:14:12.922
I could help you
do this, but you

00:14:12.922 --> 00:14:14.130
