00:14:14.130 --> 00:14:16.550
You need to stand on
your own two feet.

00:14:16.550 --> 00:14:17.400
Eric was there.

00:14:17.400 --> 00:14:18.510
He's our manager now.

00:14:18.510 --> 00:14:20.720
And I was like, Eric, talk
to your lawyer and stuff

00:14:20.720 --> 00:14:21.220
