00:14:21.220 --> 00:14:22.120
And set up your own LLC.

00:14:22.120 --> 00:14:24.494
Whether you work with me or
not, set up your own company.

00:14:24.494 --> 00:14:26.636
Because this is your
intellectual property.

00:14:26.636 --> 00:14:28.010
And it shouldn't
be that you take

00:14:28.010 --> 00:14:29.420
this idea that somebody else--

00:14:29.420 --> 00:14:29.940
DARRYL "DMC" MCDANIELS:
DC or Marvel.

00:14:29.940 --> 00:14:30.250
EDGARDO MIRANDA
RODRIGUEZ: that they

