00:14:38.212 --> 00:14:39.419
DARRYL "DMC" MCDANIELS: Ding.

00:14:39.419 --> 00:14:40.670
Darryl Makes Comics.

00:14:40.670 --> 00:14:42.569
That was easy.

00:14:42.569 --> 00:14:45.110
EDGARDO MIRANDA-RODRIGUEZ: And
