00:15:09.940 --> 00:15:10.732
My wife is worried.

00:15:10.732 --> 00:15:12.773
Man, I been thinking about
this comic book thing.

00:15:12.773 --> 00:15:15.060
And I'm thinking to myself,
he probably has so much

