00:15:43.460 --> 00:15:45.580
Oh, my gosh,
remember "Iron Fist."

00:15:45.580 --> 00:15:46.950
DARRYL "DMC" MCDANIELS:
Remember "The Defenders." stuff

00:15:46.950 --> 00:15:48.580
that people don't
