00:16:22.070 --> 00:16:23.825
So there's probably
a guy who should

00:16:23.825 --> 00:16:27.654
have joined for Marvel or DC
and never got their chance.

00:16:27.654 --> 00:16:29.070
We want to give
them their chance.

00:16:29.070 --> 00:16:31.060
There's young people,
you know what I'm saying,

00:16:31.060 --> 00:16:33.760
there's kids and young
people, there's women.

00:16:33.760 --> 00:16:36.990
So we wanted to be
completely diverse.

00:16:36.990 --> 00:16:39.760
And Riggs was like, yo, this is
going to be easy for all three

00:16:39.760 --> 00:16:44.170
of us, because we are the
people, all of the ideas,

00:16:44.170 --> 00:16:47.670
concepts, images, all
the issues, Ed was like,

00:16:47.670 --> 00:16:49.900
