afraid to talk about.

00:16:52.140 --> 00:16:54.200
Not in a negative
way, just to sell it,

00:16:54.200 --> 00:16:55.480
like to really talk about it.

00:16:55.480 --> 00:16:58.060
We want to tell
people's real stories.

00:16:58.060 --> 00:17:01.470
In the first issue, when
all this stuff was going on

00:17:01.470 --> 00:17:05.010
in the NFL, you know, with the
players fighting the women,

00:17:05.010 --> 00:17:06.460
there's those elements in there.

00:17:06.460 --> 00:17:08.842
People actually thought we
saw the NFL thing and said,

00:17:08.842 --> 00:17:09.800
we're going to do this.

00:17:09.800 --> 00:17:11.550
No, we thought all this out.

00:17:11.550 --> 00:17:13.270
We want to talk
about these things

00:17:13.270 --> 00:17:16.329
before they become big issues,
so we could prevent it.

00:17:16.329 --> 00:17:18.780
Whether people know
it or not, when

00:17:18.780 --> 00:17:21.920
rap was-- when hip hop was
first starting in the '80s,

00:17:21.920 --> 00:17:24.450
you had Run and
DMC saying be cool.

00:17:24.450 --> 00:17:25.099
Go to school.

00:17:25.099 --> 00:17:26.807
Don't mess with drugs
and you'll be cool.

00:17:26.807 --> 00:17:29.390
You had Public Enemy
saying, fight the power.

00:17:29.390 --> 00:17:31.810
You had Paris One
saying teach yourself.

00:17:31.810 --> 00:17:36.290
The thing about our universe,
even though it was F'd up,

00:17:36.290 --> 00:17:38.490
there was poverty, crime,
people killing each other

00:17:38.490 --> 00:17:41.530
in gang fights and all
that, we were good.

00:17:41.530 --> 00:17:44.200
We were using our style.

00:17:44.200 --> 00:17:46.150
He walk in there
with those sneakers,

00:17:46.150 --> 00:17:47.570
and you going to look at him.

00:17:47.570 --> 00:17:48.560
Now is this attractive?

00:17:48.560 --> 00:17:51.310
But then when you walk over
and talk to Ed as a young man,

00:17:51.310 --> 00:17:54.270
you're not going to get the B
word and the ho word and this

00:17:54.270 --> 00:17:55.050
and that, and what's
up [INAUDIBLE]

00:17:55.050 --> 00:17:56.091
word and stuff like that.

00:17:56.091 --> 00:17:58.020
You'll be able to talk
about something good.

00:17:58.020 --> 00:18:01.230
And it goes back to the point
where even those kids that were

00:18:01.230 --> 00:18:04.420
in the gangs, even the pimps
and the pushers in our era,

00:18:04.420 --> 00:18:06.790
if they saw creativity
and positivity--

00:18:06.790 --> 00:18:08.916
You know, people used to
tell me and Run, you all

00:18:08.916 --> 00:18:10.040
got to get off that corner.

00:18:10.040 --> 00:18:11.040
You all going places.

00:18:11.040 --> 00:18:12.290
You don't need to be out here.

