world we live in now,

00:18:14.140 --> 00:18:17.950
America celebrates stupidity,
ignorance, and illiteracy.

00:18:17.950 --> 00:18:20.960
The more trouble you
get, the more women you

00:18:20.960 --> 00:18:23.820
sleep with, the more stupid
stuff you do, you celebrate it,

00:18:23.820 --> 00:18:25.570
especially if it makes us money.

00:18:25.570 --> 00:18:27.160
Our world was kind of different.

00:18:27.160 --> 00:18:30.500
We've even made iced tea
and all these guys said, wo,

00:18:30.500 --> 00:18:32.380
there's power in positivity.

