powerful things

00:53:13.230 --> 00:53:14.550
and we can end on this note.

00:53:14.550 --> 00:53:18.750
He says, you know what's
the most powerful thing

00:53:18.750 --> 00:53:20.540
about this hip hop thing?

00:53:20.540 --> 00:53:22.160
What, Chuck?

00:53:22.160 --> 00:53:25.221
He says, it's not the fact that
we're getting all this money.

00:53:25.221 --> 00:53:27.470
It's not the fact that we're
making all these records.

00:53:27.470 --> 00:53:29.761
It's not the fact that we're
making videos now, running

00:53:29.761 --> 00:53:33.622
them, setting it up so
we can get sneaker deals,

00:53:33.622 --> 00:53:35.580
and we can get endorsements
