Groove" and stuff, whatever.

00:53:38.610 --> 00:53:41.647
He said, it's the power
of our communication.

00:53:41.647 --> 00:53:43.980
It's the power that there's
always a mic in front of us.

00:53:43.980 --> 00:53:45.895
We're always on TV,
videos, and records.

00:53:45.895 --> 00:53:47.270
When that mic is
in front of you,

00:53:47.270 --> 00:53:49.420
say something
that's going to make

00:53:49.420 --> 00:53:52.920
the guy that loves you all's art
say, man, I could be something.

00:53:52.920 --> 00:53:53.770
And this and that.

00:53:53.770 --> 00:53:55.770
And I remember I was
standing there with my 40

00:53:55.770 --> 00:53:57.125
ounce of Old English.

00:53:57.125 --> 00:53:58.250
I didn't like smoking weed.

00:53:58.250 --> 00:54:01.200
